title: Adinistrative Assistant Interview
Application Type: I applied online. I interviewed at Northwestern University Alumni Relations and Development (Toronto, ON) in Mar 2017
Interview Descriptions: It all started with a phone interview and then a series of group interview. The group interview was some behavioral based questions and at the end of the day it went into some specific and work related questions. In the end it wasn't bad.
Interview Questions: Q1 - Tell me about your self?
